  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The overall aim of this study is to develop and test a psychodynamic Internet--delivered
      psychological treatment for patients with social anxiety disorder and compare its efficacy to
      a waiting list.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      Participants with social anxiety disorder (MINI telephone interview) will be recruited via
      mass media and randomly allocated to psychodynamic Internet--delivered psychological
      treatment or to a waiting list control condition.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
